lustre-release$ git grep libcfs_debug_mb
libcfs/libcfs/debug.c:static unsigned int libcfs_debug_mb;
libcfs/libcfs/debug.c:CFS_MODULE_PARM(libcfs_debug_mb, "i", uint, 0644,
libcfs/libcfs/debug.c:EXPORT_SYMBOL(libcfs_debug_mb);
libcfs/libcfs/debug.c:	unsigned int max = libcfs_debug_mb;
libcfs/libcfs/debug.c:	/* If libcfs_debug_mb is set to an invalid value or uninitialized

After a recent 'make some functions static' patch this symbol is static but exported. On x86_64 for some reason it works just fine. But on PPC we have the following:

